    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-11-24T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-11-24T19:00:00-05:00" n="322"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d322">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/11–2450: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        United States Representative at the United Nations</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-11-24T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 24, 1950—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Gadel1">Gadel</gloss> 143. Re treatment of Indians in South
                    Africa. Dept concurs recommendations <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 330
                    re opposing discussion; discouraging amendments in plenary and support of
                    request for para by para vote.</p>
                <p>Dept believes US vote in plenary shld be as follows on questionable parts of res: <list>
                        <label>
                            <hi rend="italic">a</hi>.</label>
                        <item>Vote in favor second operative para.</item>
                        <label>
                            <hi rend="italic">b</hi>.</label>
                        <item>Abstain on last para preamble.</item>
                        <label>
                            <hi rend="italic">c</hi>.</label>
                        <item>Request vote by segments on 3rd para so as to separate last
                            undesirable clause; vote against this clause.</item>
                        <label>
                            <hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</label>
                        <item>Abstain on res as whole unless both last para premable and last clause
                            para 3 eliminated. If both these sections are eliminated vote in favor
                            of the resolution as a whole.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
